snippet.title: (Another) Sims 2 Beta Footage
snippet.description:
That good ol' blurry pouring rain fiesta that we haven't been invited to, from a slightly different perspective? Yes, touching upon partially-unknown fields. However, a true Sims 2 beta digger will decide whether on not it's useful for their personal lists fed with so much whimsy. Proper efforts have been taken in order to assure this video  content's legit factor, but we of course take the responsibility in case the future make us aware of any sort of omission or lack of transparency that it potentially has.

Originally posted by *fredspider* on January 12, 2006. It's possible that the footage once belonged to the extinct Brazilian YouTube channel KachuSims but it's been summarily deleted right after its respective website's closure

https://modthesims.info/m/showthread.php?p=5648221
Once upon a time, a bunch of TS1 geeks talked over Sims 1 beta aplenty The Sims - Electronic Arts - Maxis - 2000-2004
